name: Just Odd Parking Again
description:
What could be easier than just parking your car, right?

But not in Just Odd Parking Again! Each of the 10 levels is a test of not only the straightness of the player's hands, but also his ingenuity, ingenuity and nerves 💪 Would you dare to drive a car in J.O.P.A?

P. S. This is a demo version of the project in which 5 levels are available
